- [ ] **Unit 6: Polymarket disambiguation guard**

**Goal:** Support `--polymarket-keywords "kw1,kw2"` to filter market matches; auto-skip Polymarket when topic is single-token-ambiguous and no override is provided.

**Requirements:** R7

**Dependencies:** None

